    "instruction": "Inspect error_logs.csv for entries from cmdb_id in [\"frontend-0\",\"frontend-1\",\"frontend-2\"]. Return a compact summary with: 1) per-frontend: total message count, earliest timestamp, latest timestamp; 2) top up to 10 unique message texts with their counts; 3) for each unique message indicate whether the text contains any of these substrings: ['cartservice','adservice','shippingservice','currencyservice','node-5','failed to retrieve','timeout','connection refused'] (present/absent) and show the first example row for that message (ts_local, cmdb_id, message). Limit returned rows/samples to keep output bounded (max 20 lines)."
}

